duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide psychology services with a focus on youth assessment.
Possibility of seeing therapy clients with flexibility.
Opportunity to be a faculty member for the APA-accredited Internship in Clinical Psychology and Postdoctoral Fellowship.
Supervision of other trainees, if desired.
Clinical experience with youth from diverse ages and backgrounds.

education_certification.credential: Doctoral Degree in Clinical, Counseling, or Educational/School Psychology from an APA accredited University with an Indiana license to practice psychology.
Supervisory experience preferred but not required.
Willingness to gain Indiana licensure if licensed in another state.
